feedback_text: Amazing HIIT class! The energy was incredible and I burned so many calories. Coach Sarah really pushed us to our limits in the best way possible.
Great yoga session today. Very relaxing and helped with my flexibility. Would have given 5 stars but the room was a bit warm.
The strength training class was too advanced for beginners. I felt lost and couldn't keep up. Coach Mike didn't provide enough modifications.
Best spin class ever! The music was perfect and the workout was challenging but fun. Can't wait for the next one!
The Pilates class was okay. Good workout but the instructor seemed rushed and didn't explain the moves clearly.
Incredible boxing session! Coach Alex is the best. Great technique instruction and amazing workout. Highly recommend!
Terrible experience. The Zumba class was disorganized and the instructor was late. Waste of my time and money.
Good functional training class. Challenging exercises and great variety. The coach was encouraging throughout.
Love the barre class! Such a great workout for toning. The instructor is very knowledgeable and supportive.
The cardio kickboxing was too intense and not beginner-friendly. I felt overwhelmed and left early.
Another great HIIT session! Love the variety of exercises and the energy in the room.
Perfect yoga flow today. Really helped me destress after a long day at work.
The strength class was better today but still too advanced. Need more beginner options.
Spin class was fantastic again! The playlist was amazing and the workout was perfectly challenging.
Much better Pilates session today. The instructor took time to explain each movement properly.
Boxing class was incredible! Great cardio workout and technique practice.
Zumba was better today but still not great. The instructor seemed more organized though.
Excellent functional training! Really felt the burn and the coach was motivating.
Barre class was perfect as always. Love the small class size and personal attention.
Cardio kickboxing was more manageable today. Still challenging but I could keep up better.
First time trying HIIT and I loved it! The energy was amazing and I felt so accomplished after.
Great yoga session for beginners. The instructor was very patient and explained everything clearly.
Amazing strength training class! Perfect for my fitness level and the coach was very encouraging.
The spin class was good but the bike setup was uncomfortable. Good workout though.
Pilates was great today! Really felt it in my core and the instructor was very helpful.
Boxing class exceeded my expectations! Such a great stress reliever and amazing workout.
Zumba was disappointing again. The music choices were not great and the choreography was confusing.
Functional training was challenging but fun! Great variety of exercises.
Barre class was incredible! Such a great workout for toning and flexibility.
Cardio kickboxing was okay. Good workout but the instructor could be more encouraging.
The gym is clean and well-maintained. Good variety of equipment. Could use more parking spaces.
Love the facility! Everything is clean, modern, and well-organized. Great atmosphere for working out.
The locker rooms need better maintenance. Showers are often cold and the changing area is cramped.
Good gym overall. Equipment is well-maintained but could use more variety in cardio machines.
Excellent facility! Clean, spacious, and has everything I need for my workouts.
The membership signup process was smooth. Staff was helpful and friendly.
Customer service was poor. Had to wait 30 minutes to speak with someone about my membership.
Amazing customer service! The staff went above and beyond to help me with my package upgrade.
Service was okay but could be faster. The app sometimes glitches when booking classes.
Good service overall. Quick responses to emails and helpful staff at the front desk.
Coach Sarah is incredible! She's motivating, knowledgeable, and really cares about her students' progress.
Coach Mike is good but sometimes moves too fast for beginners. Great knowledge though.
Coach Alex is the best boxing instructor I've ever had. Patient, encouraging, and very skilled.
Coach Emma needs to improve her communication. Her instructions are often unclear and rushed.
Coach David is great! Very motivating and creates fun, challenging workouts.
The premium package is worth every penny! Great variety of classes and excellent value.
The basic package is okay but limited class access. Wish I had more options.
Good value for money with the standard package. Covers all my fitness needs.
The budget package is too restrictive. Can't access most classes and equipment.
Love the VIP package! Exclusive classes, personal training sessions, and amazing perks.
